name: SUFO: Sammel Unbekannte Flugobjekte
overview: SUFO: Sammel Unbekannte Flugobjekte is a strange German language "catch it" game in which you have to catch flying saucers in your van before they hit the ground. This was developed by Ulrich Rehberg and published by Tronic Verlage GmbH in Compute mit 1985/05. You have the task of intercepting the UFO's that come from the sky with the truck. The UFO's fall from the sky at shorter and shorter intervals. Once a UFO hits the ground, you've lost the game! It is then displayed how many UFO's you have intercepted. Press the J key to play again and the N key to end the game.
